comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-11T03:06:49.578Z",maintainer-agent,"External confirmation (2026-07-11): GH-509 (pm-fjxm) independently requests the fleet worker loop this item protects — bounded candidate-walk on claim race loss. A walk WITHOUT the Decision-skip this item specifies makes the hazard strictly worse: every race loser advances down the ready queue and lands on the Decision item, so the funnel-into-one-ADR failure becomes the common path, not the unlucky one. pm-fjxm's AC references this item; sequencing preference: land eqk0's Decision-skip before or with fjxm's walk."
body: ""
